    {
      "assetId": "phys.meas.scalars-vectors/teaching_note/3",
      "kind": "teaching_note",
      "conceptId": "phys.meas.scalars-vectors",
      "title": "Prerequisite Check",
      "content": "**PRE-1 — SI Units** (requires phys.meas.units)\n\nStimulus: \"What unit measures mass? What unit measures time?\"\n\nExpected: kilogram (kg); second (s)\n\nSIGNAL:INCORRECT → prerequisite gap; schedule phys.meas.units session first\n\n---",
      "localKey": null,
